  <summary date="2022-08-10T13:00:34Z" status="Introduced in House">Emergency Child and Adult Nutrition Assistance Act of 2021

This bill provides funding for and extends through June 2021 programs that, during the COVID-19 emergency, reimburse certain operational costs of child and adult care food programs and school meals programs. Under the bill, funding allocated to states remains available through FY2022.</summary>
